==反应==
该工具更多侧重于项目的表现能力和实际发挥效果。此后，[[美国国会|美国国会]]的反应也被视为该项目评估定级工具的组成内容<ref>{{cite web| author=Amelia Gruber| title=OMB seeks agency outreach on linking performance to budgets| publisher=govexec.com| date=March 4, 2004| url=http://www.govexec.com/dailyfed/0304/030404a1.htm| accessdate=2006-12-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060510122959/http://www.govexec.com/dailyfed/0304/030404a1.htm| archive-date=2006-05-10| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一项分析认为，PART的运用得到了众多预算项目的支持，特别是中型和小型项目<ref name="hello">{{cite journal | language = en | author = Gilmour, J.B. & Lewis, D.E | title = Assessing performance budgeting at OMB: the influence of politics, performance, and program size | url =  | journal = Journal of Public Administration Research and Theory | volume = 16 | issue =  | pages = 169-186 | year = 2006 | id =  }}</ref>。另外一份分析主张该项目工具实际强化了[[美国行政管理和预算局|美国行政管理和预算局]]的控制力，使其基于[[美国总统|美国总统]]的立场上对各预算项目负责监督<ref>{{cite journal | language = en | author = Dull, M | title = Why PART? The institutional politics of presidential budget reform | url =  | journal = Journal of Public Administration Research and Theory | volume = 16 | issue =  | pages = 187-215 | year = 2006 | id =  }}</ref>。

该项目赢得了2005年政府发明网络奖，相似的评估项目也在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]和[[泰国|泰国]]得到了运用<ref>{{cite web| author=| title=Program Assessment Rating Tool| publisher=Government Innovators Network| date=January 1, 2006| url=http://www.innovations.harvard.edu/awards.html?id=7496| accessdate=2006-12-15| archive-date=2014-02-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202181016/http://www.innovations.harvard.edu/awards.html?id=7496| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2007年，[[中国|中国]][[上海|上海]][[浦东新区|浦东新区]]张江高科技园区“相约张江”会议体系的评价也适用了类似的项目评估定级工具<ref>{{cite web| language =中文| publisher =中国发展研究基金会| title =项目定级评价工具在中国的初步实践| url =http://www.pbgchina.cn/newsinfo.asp?newsid=2971| author =苟燕楠| date =2009-01-15| accessdate =2009-02-02}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

